00:00:39.770 --> 00:00:45.579
in boiling water or grilling the poor guys),
the astaxanthin pigments are hidden because

00:00:45.579 --> 00:00:50.120
they are covered with other protein chains
that give their shells the bluish-gray or

00:00:50.120 --> 00:00:51.880
brownish-green color we see.

00:00:51.880 --> 00:00:57.199
Exposure to heat destroys this protein coating,while
the carotenoid pigment, astaxanthin still

00:00:57.199 --> 00:00:58.219
remains stable.

00:00:58.219 --> 00:01:02.489
